page turner and thought provoking , n.king , ca the author has a unique way of keeping you captivated and he will renew your thoughts about wolves . this book was recommended , it was not something i would have read , but after reading it i could hardly put it down , i found myself clued to this book , very funny and touching at the same time . this by far was the most revealing book about wild animals i have ever read . you will not regret reading this book ; i bought 3 others after reading it .